    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3368705/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3368705-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3368705/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">高山</span>
